 1→//! Coverage-guided boundary search for unknown/opaque constraints.
 2→//!
 3→//! When Z3 cannot solve a branch constraint (Unknown or timeout), and we have
 4→//! concrete inputs that took both sides of the branch, interpolate between
 5→//! those witnesses using binary-search-style narrowing to find the decision
 6→//! boundary. More effective than blind `fuzz_inputs()` because the search has
 7→//! directional signal from observed branch outcomes.
 8→
